Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess I pulled an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The last time I wrote a novel for fun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,was when I was publishing on the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was so interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um, Masamune-kun? Wh-When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been here for quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.36,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\i1\pos(647.483,149.777)\frz314.7}Dragon Brain{\i0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.36,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\i1\frz313.6\pos(634.233,311.555)}Izumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I had lost my composure a bit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How was my "shelved" story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It really was interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It makes me happy when you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was so interesting,\NI just kept reading right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pulled an all-nighter writing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.67,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20\frz304.8\move(443.683,87.111,503.75,163.555,1,500)}"Silverwolf of Reincarnation\NAfter-Story"\NIzumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The new piece I promised you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The continuation of Silverwolf!\NThat was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And it's really thick, too. This is like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will read it right away!\NThank you, Masamune-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}To Beloved Izumi-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't get up soon,\NI'll play a trick on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Data. Just gathering data.\NWe did some yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Collecting data on typical situations\Nby acting them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was a close one, Masamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Senpai, what's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Actually, I was helping out\Npreparing some breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I cannot have that Yankee\Ndominating the honor of home-cooked meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn this girl with 8th Grade Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How dare you interrupt at such a timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, stop calling Elf a Yankee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai, you can cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I can cook as much as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I cannot make feasts like the one last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I think I can put up a fight against\Nthe Yankee if it is Japanese food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It will be ready soon,\Nso please come to the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks like this is my loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Emily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um, M-Masamune?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I just tried saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't surprise me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you want to die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't get so mad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course I'll get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you to use that name only\Nwhen you're going to propose to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you using it so lightheartedly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. You were so calm right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It felt like yesterday's thing was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream! I tried so hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd be furious if it never even happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, as you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine. Let's head out to the beach\Nafter we eat breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We all played together yesterday,\Nso let's do some work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After we eat breakfast,\Nit's time for slightly lewd beach swim part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll have barbeque for lunch, and then a\Nstrolling date with Elf-sensei in the Fairy Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After the sun sets, we have a courage test\Nand fireworks, and the night will be tee-hee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Oh no, I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, Sensei, let's put\Nsome effort in until breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That game supervision is so behind\Nit's not even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! Help me, Masamune! I didn't come\Nto an island on the south seas to work! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You look so amused reading that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. It is the epitome of amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I see you happily reading,\Nsomehow it makes me happy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hm? What, what? Do you have\Nthe hots for Muramasa or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You gonna date her? Or even marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That is an enticing suggestion,\Nbut probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-san seems to be\Nin love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do you know that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you think we don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The story you submitted to\Nthe Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,was about you and Masamune, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you read that, it's a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That means... M-My readers also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-chan, I'm sure word of your pure,\Nfirst love went around to all your readers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Muramasa-sensei is confessing\Nher love through a story! So cute!" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Actually, the "search for Muramasa-sensei's\Npartner" is causing quite a stir on the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, and there was a round-up\Non the internet with the title,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Senju Muramasa-sensei's First Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To tell the truth,\NI was the one who made that round-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I do not care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine! Now that the cat is out of the bag,\Nthere is no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am in love with Masamune-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I do not feel embarrassed at all\Nwith these romantic feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai, you're awesome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But please stop, because it embarrasses me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,While we are at it, I shall disclose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I went along with the Yankee's ploy\Nto come to this island
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,not just to read Masamune-kun's\N"shelved" stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She said I can sit next to Masamune-kun\Non the rides to and from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-And, there might be chances\Nto chat all alone if we went on a trip together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune, don't be fooled\Nby Muramasa's simple cuteness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When she's alone in her room, I'm pretty sure\Nshe mumbles with an imaginary-Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup. I see. That's how it is for you,\NMasamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For Me? Me... well, hehe, that's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of all things, that can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right, Muramasa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-Wait, it's true?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that... bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. Can you stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt, but I'd like\NYamada-sensei to concentrate on her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Looks like you're done reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just like you said,\Nit was a "super-interesting piece of junk"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is a "super-interesting piece of junk"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A story where all the characters who died\Nin the Silverwolf series comes back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and lives happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it was interesting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This was what I've been wanting to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I will be away for about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you dare goof off while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will never goof off from my work, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's time to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't do your work,\Nwon't you get scolded later?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just a little bit! Come on, come on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I really love how you are so easily persuaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, what shall we do?\NSomething that ends quickly would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, we should play the King's Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? Th-The King's Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa, you're going to play, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen up, Muramasa-chan.\NIn a King's Game....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And there, you can make Masamune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh my, such a thing is possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Masamune-kun,\Nwe shall play the King's Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll use these instead of picking straws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, all of you, draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the King if you draw a King card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can give any command to the people\Nwho drew the numbers from 1 to 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What should the first command be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First, let's try things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Number 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...kisses number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn you! That wasn't the plan\Nyou discussed with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I even told you my number!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, planning things out beforehand is unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since one person dropped out, we will replenish\None member to resume the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard there's a King's Game.\NI can't say no to that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you can't pick a card over Skype, right?\NHow would we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, let's just have\NEromanga-sensei always be King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What, really? Is that okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, let's draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. Make any command!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From this instant, we are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...servants to the Great King Eromanga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I don't know anyone\Nwith such a dangerous name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see...\NNumber 3, take off a piece of clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Elf-chan, that's unfair.\NYou've got a swimsuit on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought something like this might happen!\NI'm glad I was ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So unfair! Though you look cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, next turn, Great King Eromanga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number 1...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...tell me what kind of panties you're wearing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong? Muramasa-chan,\Nwhat kind of panties are you wearing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Muramasa, you must—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you say any further, I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Muramasa-chan, can it be that you're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...not wearing panties?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It is because, this kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is because I am wearing a kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, it's turned into a really awkward game\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kunimitsu, you betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You tattled on Aniki that we were goofing off\Nand playing the King's Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not it! I just happened\Nto bump into Chris-san over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Sorry I doubted—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh? So you were goofing off and playing\Nthe King's Game instead of working?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You are so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you follow\NMuramasa-sensei's example a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please don't compare me with someone\Nwho has stories
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,springing out of her fingertips\Njust by breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry you had to play along\Nwith the whims of one of our authors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, what you're writing there, Sensei,\Ncould it be Demon Sword volume 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't write novels anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Wow, so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Here, have some shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}This really goes well with the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You get just the shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What in the whorrle ish going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWait, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems like you're really drunk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm totawwy fwine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, what Muramasha-shan\Nshaid earwier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where you shaid\Nyou won't write novelsh any-moh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you sherioush?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No wai! Why're you gonna qwit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because my dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To acquire lots of stories I feel is the most\Ninteresting in the world. That was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I was writing novels for that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I realized something during this camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If Masamune-kun writes novels for me like this,\NI no longer have to write any myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A novel nut like her\Nwon't be able to stop writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, it won't even last overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When she sleeps and wakes up,\Nshe'll have second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That makes me sound like a nutcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just said you were a novel nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You seem to want to say something, Kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. More like something I want to tell you\Nrather than something I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.53,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10}From: Hana Umezono
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun, what did you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before I do that,\NI wanted to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.50,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10\fs20\frz323.4\move(281.15,228.445,348.284,300.445,5,797)}Hana Umezono\NChiba Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.91,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10\fs20\frz323.4\pos(356.233,307.556)}Hana Umezono\NChiba Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My most treasured of fan letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I-I see... Oh, a fan letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's someone who always sends me\Nreally passionate fan letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The newest one I received had 50 pages in it.\NIsn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.31,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz327.1\pos(315.6,99.555)}Hana Umezono\NChiba Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The sender seems to be a middle-school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}She even draws illustrations in colored pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:35.53,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs30\frz28.66\t(150,4000,\fscx90\fscy90)\move(181.584,94.223,197.484,109.334,3,4590)}Izumi-sensei,\NI'm always cheering for you.\NI drew Beniusagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Do you always carry\Nyour fan letters with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just got this from my editor. I brought it\Nbecause I wanted to read it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That, and, I wanted to show it to you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Ever since my debut,\Nshe has consistently sent me letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I read them over and over again,\Nand they've always cheered me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even when I couldn't publish anything,\Nand times were rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even when my books had bad hype\Nand I got depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks to this person,\NI could hold my head high,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,knowing my stories were interesting\Nand they were worth writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were the one who sent me\Nthese fan letters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No, it was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You sent me the handwritten manuscript for\NDemon Sword volume 12 the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I noticed right away\Nthat the handwriting was identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can only think of one middle-school female fan\Nof mine with such beautiful handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you have found me out,\NI guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But what does that have to do\Nwith whatever you wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the longest time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I always wanted to tell you how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To tell the person\Nwho enjoys my stores so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And now, my wish I've had\Nfrom when I debuted finally came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your dream was to turn your novels\Ninto an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and watch it together\Nwith your younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I do have that, too. But, what I talked about\Njust now is a different dream from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A different dream? I-Is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course it's okay\Nto have as many dreams as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, don't you think it's a shame to stop writing\Njust because one of your dreams came true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll stop writing\Neven if that other dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because I have someone who sends me\Nfan letters that make me feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm at least a million points out of a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I made up my mind, Masamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Writing the most interesting novel in the world,\Nand reading it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will now try to make that wish come true\Nwith my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That "I won't write novels" statement\Ndidn't last hours, let alone a whole night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That Yankee's predictions were totally off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just now, I have found a new dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My "new dream" is something\Nthat I cannot turn into reality alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I cannot give you the details, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the time being, I shall have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...fall in love with me.
